
-After you close the incident, when state is set to resolved or closed complete, a survey should be triggered.

-Type 'trigger conditions' in the filter navigator and you can check the conditions for surveys
-Q: so I see them in the table?
-A: yes

-and also you can check questions in surveys
-so then they are assessment metrics

Step One: Look up “Trigger Conditions” in the Application Navigator.

Step Two: Click on “Assessment”

Step Three: Scroll down to “Survey Instances.”

Step Four: Go to “Trigger ID: INC######”

Step Five: Test out a ticket (either Incident, the Change Request, ect).

Step Six: Look to see if a new assessment was triggered under your ticket number.
